- 🎓 I'm an **Energy Science & Engineering** student at **IIT Bombay** (2024 - 2028).
- 🔭 I’m currently working on **Energy Analytics**, **Solar & Wind Power Forecasting**, and **Deep Learning (CNN-LSTM)**.
- 🌱 I’m constantly exploring deeper into **Microgrid Design**, **Robotics**, and **Finance Strategies**.
